# Per-index eval dumps are large (~2 MB each); the small *_SUMMARY.json point
# estimates ARE committed so figures/tables regenerate. Analysis defaults to
# point estimates (SKIP_BOOTSTRAP=True in tofu_scores.py / muse_scores.py); set
# it False with these restored to recompute the 99% bootstrap CIs.
*_EVAL.json
TOFU_EVAL.json.*
MUSE_EVAL.json.*
bootstrap_cache.json*

# Cluster + tooling logs
slurm-*.out
*.log

# Hydra / misc
.hydra/
.DS_Store
